    <string name="countdown_explanation">This screen demonstrates the inactivity time out capability of
        Workspace ONE software development kit (SDK) for Android. The timer
        counts down the inactivity period, if one is specified by policy. When
        the timer finishes, the user interface will be blocked by the SDK until
        the passcode is entered.
        \nTapping the timer qualifies as activity and will restart the
        time out. Note that the countdown display doesn\'t read its value from
        the SDK.</string>
